abstract: The search giant’s surging third quarter profits showed that it was growing at twice the speed of the online advertising market, which itself is booming.
snippet: The search giant’s surging third quarter profits showed that it was growing at twice the speed of the online advertising market, which itself is booming.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, Oct. 18 — The gap between Google and its rivals keeps getting larger.

headline.main: Google’s Strong Quarter Widens Gap With Rivals
